data.title: ADF Careers
data.meta_description: Considering an exciting  career in the Air Force? Discover our story, our people, our locations, priority role, training and the Air Force Reserves.
data.text:
Up there? That's where you'll push the limits of what's possible in a career in Air Force.

Join the Air Force and be part of a diverse and supportive team that alongside the Navy and Army, defends our nation, our people, our values and our way of life. This is achieved by controlling the air, acquiring intelligence through reconnaissance and surveillance, providing air mobility for all operational needs, and supporting combat missions through strike capability.

Work with

world-leading

technology

Working in Air Force, you’ll push the limits of what’s possible on the ground, in the air, or up in space. You’ll work with world-leading technology in a range of areas, which could include monitoring satellites, or working on projects for new space-based capabilities in Defence Space Command.

In return for your skills and positive attitude, the ADF will set you up with everything you need for a role in leadership, tech, engineering, cyber, communications, logistics or catering.
